The Java program for the above Inverted half Pyramid star pattern:

I have created a public class named HalfPyramid 
I have defined the main method to begin the execution
I am starting the for loop to print the pyramid.
I am printing the star symbol.
Finally, I am printing the Invertedpyramid Star .

